43.000Z","msg":"有人話自殺死咗之後<br />\n會不斷重複自殺動作<br />\n直到本身嘅陽壽已盡<br />\n<br />\n死咗好多嘢都未知<br />\n如果件事係真嘅話<br />\n你會用一生搵愛人<br />\n定係一生不停自殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"362d59a7db2b32bcdf672e3666dac38159affcae","tid":2443141,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f80f13955bb5925308bae42de1eee47eebbe47be","tid":2443141,"uid":5930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a80ca00d786330b2d298fe15fd78365afdbd26a","tid":2443141,"uid":194370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"679167e43349d26c62c417e502a856fe7c566dd0","tid":2443141,"uid":5930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:18:45.000Z","msg":"我覺得思想上好大折磨係仲死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:28:22.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n如果連呼吸都係痛苦冇得避<br />\n其實有啲問題真係冇辦法解決到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T07:29:09.000Z","msg":"冇辦法解決到點解仲要逼我面對？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:04:38.000Z","msg":"你係巴打定絲打？"},{"pid":"aafdcbb30ac1c44490eefcced3573f0b28bdf22b","tid":2443141,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:04:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oEE0JaT-QVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoEE0JaT-QVs&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=b92cc881\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oEE0JaT-QVs</a><br />\n只能夠講諗到自殺嘅人，果下嘅無力感同壓力真係大到無希望先會做<br />\n雖然我無去到咁極端想自殺，但只係想講可能撐多陣會有啲唔同，呢個世界仲好多地方未去過"},{"pid":"c532465c98b710e9616f4367db395c86c168e4ce","tid":2443141,"uid":5930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"362d59a7db2b32bcdf672e3666dac38159affcae","tid":2443141,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f80f13955bb5925308bae42de1eee47eebbe47be","tid":2443141,"uid":