102bf69b903cb9111fb4ad3","tid":2443141,"uid":5930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef1d5fdf89fed277ab416551a3303af1aa2a6514","tid":2443141,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb748db773ef6fbc82a61b2a710413027fb8551e","tid":2443141,"uid":5930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"857f07c75597ffc55df589b70b5cb3d227d70e59","tid":2443141,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"辛苦了<br />\n男仔活喺香港係辛苦啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"所以都係果句啦，要鼓起勇氣喺香港自殺唔係一件容易嘅事。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:07:24.000Z","msg":"仲要揀啱方法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:08:37.000Z","msg":"香港嗰班左膠/人道主義者，好鬼鍾意叫人哋樂觀啲面對呢個世界<br />\n仆你個街，我做到我就唔會想自殺啦"},{"pid":"70d5366cd6034649687a4cdb03b6d29c6454f4b8","tid":2443141,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66f7193b84965d4406aecb43eced510f478b6c18","tid":2443141,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aafdcbb30ac1c44490eefcced3573f0b28bdf22b","tid":2443141,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:04:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oEE0JaT-QVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoEE0JaT-QVs&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=b92cc881\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oEE0JaT-QVs</a><br />\n只能夠講諗到自殺嘅人，果下嘅無力感同壓力真係大到無希望先會做<br />\n雖然我無去到咁極端想自殺，但只係想講可能撐多陣會有啲唔同，呢個世界仲好多地方未去過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"活在當下享受生活, 看來你心中盛載著的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀。人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=ae587ec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（   <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw3qjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=e20b3b71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a>  ）。 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：下午4時至凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期：晚上８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"6283417b3fb220742d1fcc95688385be332502fa","tid":2443141,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2059303a4f21a345f4bdacdfe3f464bfbe089b42","tid":2443141,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaa8a4c0428f132b9678b72999e3c6a6523a6838","tid":2443141,"uid":95499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"橫掂都係死 點解唔死得型啲<br />\n例如每日食兩包煙 食到生肺癌死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8c123a3f324a830123698e4c7cc6433f4d4e81","tid":2443141,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6283417b3fb220742d1fcc95688385be332502fa","tid":2443141,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2059303a4f21a345f4bdacdfe3f464bfbe089b42","tid":2443141,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaa8a4c0428f132b9678b72999e3c6a6523a6838","tid":2443141,"uid":95499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"橫掂都係死 點解唔死得型啲<br />\n例如每日食兩包煙 食到生肺癌死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:02:13.