id":"1e252803c09970553162decec7cc4e715c40ad81","tid":2443141,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ff6c8e6338b3fc8457159f2a1910e1794bdd149","tid":2443141,"uid":211729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:25:40.000Z","msg":"你打算用咩方法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"費事講太白"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:35:49.000Z","msg":"有冇準備材料先"},{"pid":"d270f6bfcc1898856c80b91bd34254bfd7c5dbc2","tid":2443141,"uid":213028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:42:53.000Z","msg":"根據香港現行的法例，「終止無效治療」及「病人拒絕治療」都是合法的。 在香港，雖然法例中並沒有安樂死一詞，但有關安樂死的行為會在「侵害人身條例」的定義下，任何協助、教唆、慫恿或促使他人自殺的話，都會被視為犯罪行為；而任何人如因意圖殺害或傷害他人身體而殺害他人，將可列為謀殺。<br />\n<br />\n換言之 安樂死在港並未合法<br />\n只係文字游戲<br />\n<br />\n自殺合法 <br />\n<br />\n但係若果有條傻西話自殺有理隨時拉得<br />\n<br />\n住香港 <br />\n<br />\n慢性自殺"},{"pid":"a1516f0161334fcb883f74992682499a3885dc13","tid":2443141,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d57509e32f0a343ee41241973eb36c3598405a9","tid":2443141,"uid":211729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e252803c09970553162decec7cc4e715c40ad81","tid":2443141,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ff6c8e6338b3fc8457159f2a1910e1794bdd149","tid":2443141,"uid":211729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:25:40.000Z","msg":"你打算用咩方法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"費事講太白"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T13:35:49.000Z","msg":"有冇準備材料先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"要錢<br />\n同埋唔會係今年"},{"pid":"222a86a2b939a9600278b1ab948d82b758d0fadc","tid":2443141,"uid":211729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1516f0161334fcb883f74992682499a3885dc13","tid":2443141,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d57509e32f0a343ee41241973eb36c3598405a9","tid":2443141,"uid":211729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e252803c09970553162decec7cc4e715c40ad81","